Privacy policy
The purpose of this policy is to maintain the privacy of and protect the personal information of vendors, (and/or any of their employees), partners, members, end-users of TransUnion CIBIL Limited (“we”, “us”, “our”, “TransUnion CIBIL”) or any other individual whose personal information we receive and to ensure compliance with all laws applicable to us.
The contents of this privacy policy ("Privacy Policy") along with the general terms and conditions ("General TNC") available at
