and
http://www.cibil.com
any other channels such as mobile application (“Websites”).
You hereby acknowledge of having read and accepted the terms of the Privacy Policy by use of this Website and/or otherwise by virtue of expressly consenting to provide us with your personal information. The capitalized terms used herein and not defined shall have the meaning set out in the General TNC.
TransUnion CIBIL’s Privacy Statement
